duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide dental hygiene services to patients including perio charting, sterilization, room setup/cleanup, and other related duties.
Work as a team player to assist the dental team in providing excellent patient care.
Maintain honesty, thoroughness, and professionalism in all aspects of the job.
Quickly learn and adapt to the office's policies and procedures.

education_certification.credential: Associate's degree in Dental Hygiene (Bachelor's preferred)
